---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';

const title = "Hand Wash Fort Lauderdale | Mobile Service | Route95";
const description = "Professional mobile hand wash in Fort Lauderdale. We come to you! Two-bucket method, pH-balanced soap, no scratches. Same-day service. Call 754-215-2272";

const parentCategory = {
  href: "/car-wash-fort-lauderdale/",
  title: "Car Wash Services"
};
---

<ServiceLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  h1="Hand Wash Fort Lauderdale"
  intro="Professional hand washing removes dirt safely without scratching your paint, unlike automated car washes that damage clear coats over time."
  currentPage="/hand-wash-fort-lauderdale/"
  parentCategory={parentCategory}
>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">
      <section>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Route95 brings mobile hand wash service directly to your Fort Lauderdale home or office. We use the two-bucket method trusted by professional detailers worldwide, combined with pH-balanced Chemical Guys soap that lifts grime without stripping your existing wax protection.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Automatic car washes might be convenient, but those spinning brushes collect dirt and drag it across your paint hundreds of times. The result is swirl marks and micro-scratches that dull your finish. Our hand wash process treats your vehicle the way it deserves to be treated.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          We serve all of Fort Lauderdale including Las Olas, Nurmi Isles, Seven Isles, and surrounding Broward County areas. Same-day appointments are often available.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">How Much Does a Hand Wash Cost in Fort Lauderdale?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>A professional mobile hand wash in Fort Lauderdale typically costs between $30 and $50 depending on your vehicle size.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Sedans and coupes fall at the lower end of that range. SUVs, trucks, and larger vehicles cost a bit more due to additional surface area. We provide exact pricing when you call based on your specific vehicle.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          The investment pays off when you consider the cost of paint correction to remove swirl marks from automated washes. One trip through a tunnel wash can cause damage that costs hundreds to fix.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">How Long Does a Hand Wash Take?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>A complete hand wash takes approximately 30 to 45 minutes depending on vehicle size and how dirty it is.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          We don't rush through the process like automated washes that cycle cars through in minutes. Each panel gets individual attention. We wash from top to bottom, rinse our mitts frequently, and ensure no dirt gets dragged across your paint. Since we come to you, this time doesn't cost you anything.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Why Choose Hand Washing Over Automated Car Washes?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Hand washing is the only safe method to clean your vehicle without causing paint damage from brushes and recycled water.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Here's what happens at automated car washes:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Spinning brushes collect dirt and debris from previous vehicles</li>
          <li>That grit gets dragged across your paint, creating fine scratches</li>
          <li>Recycled water contains contaminants that deposit on your surface</li>
          <li>Harsh detergents strip wax and dry out rubber seals</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Our hand wash process eliminates all these problems. Fresh microfiber mitts glide gently across your paint. Clean water rinses away contaminants. pH-balanced soap cleans without stripping protection.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Our Hand Wash Process</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold flex-shrink-0">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f]">Pre-Rinse</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We thoroughly rinse your vehicle to remove loose dirt, sand, and debris before any contact washing.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold flex-shrink-0">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f]">Two-Bucket Wash</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">One bucket holds clean soapy water. The second bucket is for rinsing our wash mitt. This prevents reintroducing dirt to your paint.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold flex-shrink-0">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f]">Panel-by-Panel Cleaning</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We wash one section at a time, working from top to bottom. Each panel gets fresh soap solution.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold flex-shrink-0">4</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f]">Rinse and Dry</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">A complete rinse removes all soap. We hand dry with clean microfiber towels to prevent water spots.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold flex-shrink-0">5</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f]">Final Inspection</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We check every panel for missed spots, water spots, or areas needing extra attention.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <aside class="lg:col-span-1">
      <div class="sticky top-24 space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Hand Wash Quick Facts</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-[#c9a227] font-bold">$</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600">$30-$50 depending on size</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">30-45 minutes</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Two-bucket method</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">pH-balanced soap</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Scratch-free finish</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-xl p-6 text-white">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4">Book Your Hand Wash</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
            Same-day appointments available throughout Fort Lauderdale.
          </p>
          <a href="tel:+17542152272" class="btn-accent w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
            </svg>
            754-215-2272
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Related Services</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><a href="/car-waxing-fort-lauderdale/" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Car Waxing</a></li>
            <li><a href="/clay-bar-treatment-fort-lauderdale/" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Clay Bar Treatment</a></li>
            <li><a href="/wheel-cleaning-fort-lauderdale/" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Wheel Cleaning</a></li>
            <li><a href="/full-detail-fort-lauderdale/" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Full Detail</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</ServiceLayout>
